<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<title>Aperçu des Informations du Candidat</title>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; background-color: #f7fafc; padding: 20px;">

		<div style="max-width: 1600px; margin: 0 auto;">
			<div style="background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
				<div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">
					<img src="{{ asset('/images/cameroon.png')}}" alt="Cameroon Flag" style="height: 56px;">
					<img src="/images/uiecc_logo.png" alt="UIECC Logo" style="height: 112px;">
					<img src="/images/congo.png" alt="Congo Flag" style="height: 56px;">
				</div>

				<div style="border: 4px solid #2f855a; border-radius: 16px; padding: 16px;">
					<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">
						<h2 style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0;">UNIVERSITE INTER-ETATS CAMEROUN-CONGO</h2>
						<h3 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0;">RECIPISSE DE DEPOT DE DOSSIER</h3>
					</div>

					<div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
						<div style="flex: 1;">
							<div style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
								<span style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a202c; width: 66%;">No Dossier:</span>
								<span style="color: #e53e3e; font-weight: 600;">***************</span>
							</div>
							<div style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
								<span style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a202c; width: 66%;">Filiere choisie:</span>
								<span style="font-weight: 600;">{{ candidate.field }}</span>
							</div>
							<div style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
								<span style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a202c; width: 66%;">Session du concours:</span>
								<span style="font-weight: 600;">2024</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div style="width: 160px; height: 160px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; background-color: #e2e8f0; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
							<span style="display: block; height: 160px; width: 160px;">
								{% if candidate.photo %}
									<img src="{{ asset('uploads/photos/' ~ candidate.photo) }}" alt="Photo du candidat" style="height: 160px; width: 160px; object-fit: cover;">
								{% else %}
									<div class="rounded-full h-32 w-32 bg-gray-300 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500">
										<span class="text-4xl">?</span>
									</div>
								{% endif %}
							</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div style="margin-top: 40px;">
						<div style="background-color: #2f855a; color: white; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; text-align: center;">
							<h4 style="font-weight: 600; margin: 0;">INFORMATIONS SUR LE CONCOURS</h4>
						</div>
						<div style="border: 1px solid #2f855a; padding: 40px 24px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
							<div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
								<div style="flex: 1; margin-right: 40px;">
									<div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
										<span style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a202c;">Nom et Prenoms:</span>
										<span style="font-weight: 600;">{{ candidate.name }}</span>
									</div>
									<div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
										<span style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a202c;">Date de naissance:</span>
										<span style="font-weight: 600;">{{ candidate.dateOfBirth|date('d/m/Y') }}</span>
									</div>
									<div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
										<span style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a202c;">Nationalité:</span>
										<span style="font-weight: 600;">{{ candidate.nationality }}</span>
									</div>
									<div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
										<span style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a202c;">Centre d'Examen (Lieu de depot du dossier):</span>
										<span style="font-weight: 600;">{{ candidate.examinationCenter }}</span>
									</div>
									<div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
										<span style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a202c;">Langue de Composition:</span>
										<span style="font-weight: 600;">{{ candidate.language }}</span>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div style="flex: 1;">
									<div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
										<span style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a202c;">Sexe:</span>
										<span style="font-weight: 600;">{{ candidate.sexe }}</span>
									</div>
									<div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
										<span style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a202c;">Lieu de naissance:</span>
										<span style="font-weight: 600;">{{ candidate.placeOfBirth }}</span>
									</div>
									<div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
										<span style="display: block; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a202c;">Diplome presente | Serie:</span>
										<span style="font-weight: 600;">{{ candidate.certificate }}</span>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div style="margin-top: 48px; text-align: right;">
						<div style="text-align: center;">
							<span style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 10px;">SIGNATURE DU RECEPTEUR</span>
							<div style="width: 224px; height: 112px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin-top: 8px;"></div>
						</div>
						<div style="font-size: 10px; font-style: italic; margin-top: 48px;">
							<span>Imprimee le
								{{ "now"|date("d F Y, h:i a") }}</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d;">
					<p>Ce document est généré automatiquement. Veuillez ne pas le modifier.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</body>
</html>
